\left(\begin{matrix} u_1'\\ u_2' \end{matrix}\right)=\left(\begin{matrix} -1 & 1\\ 0 & -1 \end{matrix}\right) \left(\begin{matrix} u_1\\ u_2 \end{matrix}\right)
